prompts.frontCover: A minimalist 2D illustration on a clean white background. In the center, a single, elegantly simple cartoon birthday candle, drawn with clean black lines. The flame on the candle has been playfully replaced by a tiny, charmingly drawn cartoon dumpster, also in simple black line art, with small, whimsical orange and yellow flames peeking out from inside it. Below this illustration, in a beautiful, readable, and elegant handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Welcome to the dumpster fire."
